<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p>Welcome to your monthly place to talk about anything and everything to do with our music scene. Indie, EDM, metal, classical, soul, jazz, hip hop, dub&#39;n&#39;bass, jungle punk, it doesn&#39;t matter as long as it&#39;s in or from Toronto.</p> <p>Tell us about local acts you&#39;ve seen or discovered, new singles and albums from local artists you love, upcoming gigs and anything else. If you&#39;re an artist or you&#39;re in a band, tell us about yourselves, what you play and where we can see you. Feel free to promote yourselves with links to your Bandcamp, Soundcloud, Spotify, YouTube or anything else.</p> <p>Summer is finally almost here, and the festivals and open air gigs are starting to get under way. Let&#39;s hear what&#39;s happening.</p> <p>If it&#39;s music and it&#39;s in Toronto, we want to know about it!</p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/j0hnnyengl1sh"> /u/j0hnnyengl1sh </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/toronto/comments/bwe7ed/toronto_music_scene_june/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/toronto/comments/bwe7ed/toronto_music_scene_june/">[comments]</a></span>